Gordon Mohr &lt;gojomo@...&gt; wrote:
          Jigar Patel wrote:
&gt; Hi, Here I provide my order.xml
&gt; 
&gt; Here I used following Rules and Its crawling redirected pages...
&gt; 
&gt; I want to make sure that I am doing correct or not ?
&gt; 
&gt; Here I need only Text/Html content and Do not need Embed link [E]...
&gt; 
